<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1423434-one-of-the-illustrations-the-one-with-the">One of the illustrations, the one with the toys, shows what looks to be a spice rack in the background. The names on the jars are not in English and include &quot;káya&quot; and &quot;houska&quot; (the other two could be only parts of words and look like possibly &quot;cuka&quot; and &quot;hrách&quot;). Google Translate is failing me. Does anyone recognize these words and their language?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
